				<div><span class="category"><a href="http://www.geekosystem.com/category/hug-it-out/">Hug It Out</a></span></div>				<h1 id="meebo-title">Celebrate Father&#8217;s Day The Meme Way With Troll Dad</h1>
				<p class="tags" style="width:490px;"><a href="http://www.geekosystem.com/tag/fathers-day/" rel="tag">fathers day</a> <a href="http://www.geekosystem.com/tag/meme/" rel="tag">meme</a> <a href="http://www.geekosystem.com/tag/troll-dad/" rel="tag">Troll Dad</a></p>
				<div class="tweet-button">
          <a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button">&nbsp;</a>
          <script type="text/javascript"><!--
